,"text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2cc818b0-f971-431c-851a-333ba5a6dac1","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have received the shirts together with the other things mentioned in the letter. Thank\u00A0Cassandra on my behalf, which thou wilt know how\u00A0to do without any prompting from me.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"76333815-a139-4374-adbc-d6e46a84f617","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5359a7cf-5c8d-489c-b50f-15b3237045e6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"13387acb-d86e-4318-afd1-ed9e155d4133","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2efebce1-fa8a-430e-8c22-106e04df3497","type":"codex/claim-reference","start":19,"end":26,"value":"1058db64-b09c-4c4d-bacb-02bf1081038f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2ae079ee-3622-4c5f-8acd-18ac36eb2cdb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":32,"end":37,"value":"1b2caa85-35e0-4e79-891c-26ee34287f1d","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0b381d4f-3f4e-4a6a-be61-73faa7205508","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":101,"end":109,"value":"406b9dc0-8e0d-46e3-bfd8-aeb93346e8be","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"cf64473b-daad-49b6-8f69-c52a49881926","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":114,"end":115,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7cbcab50-92a2-44a1-945a-ca6eb263a4cf","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":131,"end":134,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7538d617-442c-4b6a-b276-e6e41900a63b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":183,"end":184,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bb5c17f6-3b60-429f-aedd-9132a980820a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b928730f-6908-4f26-8c7e-a208e4122872","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"I have received two letters, both of which exhort me in pressing terms to return to Florence. I think thou canst not be aware that some four months ago I received permission from the Duke of Florence, through the medium of the Cardinal da Carpi, who\u00A0is one of the building committee of St. Peter\u0027s [De\u0027\u00A0Deputati della Fabrica di Santo Pietro], to continue the erection of the said St. Peter\u0027s at Rome. I thanked God from the bottom of my heart for this mercy and was exceedingly pleased: now thou writest to me so warmly on the subject, as I have already said, that I do not know whether thy letters are the outcome of\u00A0thy desire that I should return to Florence, or whether\u00A0the situation has changed. Therefore explain thyself\u00A0more fully, because all these things trouble and vex my peace of mind.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6799f5c9-183f-46d3-aecb-ce6ffb194a64","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":0,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"37b0a27b-b41e-48de-993a-becc82a2315a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":50,"end":51,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7917173b-d522-4407-9ee0-252d39bf072e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":81,"end":82,"value":"7ae3c69b-e4c4-4f42-8902-aaf9ad5d0eb9","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"373bc588-0bf9-4db2-a9fe-4d5abaec6f35","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":84,"end":91,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3acca340-62d0-4c5a-855d-ac09745754fb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":94,"end":94,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"42b92004-9ae3-4156-a9d8-15d152f66949","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":